{"tid":1868542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【RFA報導】支持香港示威者 廣州楊旭彬被控尋覓滋事","createTime":"2020-02-07T15:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T16:45:15.000Z","uid":288648,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6defc6862a3c2ec74ec727526975f784c6c76017","tid":1868542,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cArYSoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcArYSoP.jpg&h=8a442a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年8月底，楊旭彬在廣州海珠區小洲村一帶多處塗噴&ldquo;時代革命&rdquo;、&ldquo;光復廣州&rdquo;、&ldquo;廣東獨立&rdquo;、&ldquo;支持HK&quot;、&ldquo;自由&rdquo;、&ldquo;民主&rdquo;等字樣的標語， 當日被捕。 被捕時，從家中搜出防毒面具、頭盔、噴油等物品。 他被控尋釁滋事罪，起䜣書指楊旭彬在街頭噴塗上述反動標語，造成群眾圍觀，是無視國家法律，在公共場所起哄鬧事，擾亂了社會秩序。 案件已於2020年1月13日開庭，候判。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 楊旭彬生於1980年，廣東揭陽人，畢業於廣州美術學院，自由職業。 楊旭彬被捕前在他的實名推特多次轉發香港 #反送中 抗爭的消息，又在其YouTube 上傳在香港拍攝的反送中抗爭影片。 他在推特上的自我簡介為&ldquo;為民主和自由而戰&rdquo;，曾發帖稱&ldquo;我們將站著死，也不跪著活&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0205a-02052020075209.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2Fwul0205a-02052020075209.html&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxnzC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=89be5aa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0205a-02052020075209.html</a>"},{"pid":"b61855363fe3686994ffe99741df4e798ac46abe","tid":1868542,"uid":288648,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"大家可以繼續覺得支那人死全家<br />\n不過佢所做嘅事 係呼應香港嘅行動<br />\n咁我覺得我可以俾大家知道一下<br />\n至少佢嘅努力有人睇到 佢所做嘅冇白費到"},{"pid":"138c1c932415842652830f29db8834ac1082ecca","tid":1868542,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e840e7b3413a9d58feb399b9d945d773eb8a6a2b","tid":1868542,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:52: